  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee runnaja Wahrdug nepateeti swehredami/ un Derribu darrtdami/ tapehz fattohs ta Sohdiba ka Nahwes Sahle us ta Ethruma Waggahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee Eedsihwotaji no Sa-marijas istruhzinafees pahr to Tettu no Bet-Awena/ jo tapa-fcha Laudis behdasees pahr to/ un winna Ramarim/ kas zitt-kahrt pahr winnu preezajahs winna Gohtibas deht/ jo ta irr no winna atswesta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir tas pats taps us As-firtju weste/ par weenu Dahwa-nu preekfch ta Kehnixa no Jare-ba/ Gewraims taps Kauna/ un Israels apkannohts fawa Pa-dohina deht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Taē Kehnisch no Sa-marijas irr bohja gahjie/ ta Put-tas Uhdens Wirru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Augstumee no A-wena/ zaur ko Israels apgreh-kojahs/ taps tsdeldeeti/ Ehrſchſki un Dadscht nahks uhs winnu Altaxeem/ un tee fazzihs uhs teem Kalneem: Apklahjeet muhs/ un uhs teem Pakalneem: Krihteet pahr muhs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Gibejas Deenahm effi tu ak Israēl! grehkojs/ tur irr tee pastahwejschi/ ta Kaufchana eekſch Gibejas prett teem pahr-wehrtiteem Behrneem tohs ne fagrahbs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas buhs man pa labbu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo Gewraims irr weens Teſch erraddis labprahrt kult/ bet es nahſchu pahr to Sta-stimu winna Kakla/ Es jahschu us Gewraimu/ Juhda ars/ un Jehkabs ezzehe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sehjeet jums par Taif-nibu/ planjeet pehz tahs Lab-darrischanas/ plehfeet juhs janu Semini/ jo Laiks irr to KUN-GU mekleht/ teekams tas nahk/ un mahza jums Taifnibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Juhs arrat Besdeeubu/ Zannadarrischanu juhs plaujat/ un ehdat Meslu Auglus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tu pakaujees us to Zettu/ us to Watrumu taivo Warrenu/ tapehz zelsees leeſs Trohkniesstarp taweem Laudin/ un wiﬁi tawee Stiprumi taps pohstiti. Itt ka Salinans to Nammu Arbeli pohstitja Kakra Laika/ fur ta Mahte ar teem Behrneem tappę fatreefta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tavatt taps jums no Be-teles darrihts juhfas niknas Biehdibas deht/ tas Israēka Kehnisch taps deldeht pascha Agrumā isdeldehts.\n"
    }
  ],
